chart.name: VCL on Host
chart.programText:
A = data('vcl.total_vcl', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).publish(label='A')
B = data('vcl.avail_vcl', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).publish(label='B')
C = data('vcl.discarded_vcl', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Overall Hit Rate %
chart.programText:
A = data('cache_result.hit', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('cache_result.miss', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/(A+B) * 100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Connection Rate/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('connections.received', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='C')
D = (A).max().publish(label='D')

chart.name: Connection States
chart.programText: A = data('connections.*', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0') and filter('plugin_instance', '*-backend')).sum(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Total Bytes/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('total_bytes.resp_body', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('total_bytes.resp_header', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A+B).publish(label='C')
D = data('total_bytes.req_body', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum().publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = data('total_bytes.req_header', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum().publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (D+E).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Session Operations/sec

chart.name: Shared Memory Operations
chart.programText: A = data('total_operations.*', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Uptime
chart.programText:
A = data('uptime.client_uptime', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).mean().publish(label='A')
B = (A/(60*60*24)).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Hit Rate %
chart.programText:
A = data('cache_result.hit', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)

C = (A/(A+B) * 100).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = data('cache_result.hitpass', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum(by=['host']).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (C).min().publish(label='E')

chart.name: Total Connection Rate/sec
chart.programText: A = data('connections.received', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish')).sum().publish(label='A')

chart.name: Bytes/request
chart.programText:
A = data('total_bytes.resp_body', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('total_bytes.resp_header', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
G = data('connections.received', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).mean().publish(label='G', enable=False)
C = ((A+B)/G).mean().publish(label='C')
D = data('total_bytes.req_body', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = data('total_bytes.req_header', filter=filter('plugin', 'varnish') and filter('host', 'integration-test-varnish-4.0.3-0')).publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = ((D+E)/G).mean().publish(label='F')
